Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
A ranar Alhamis, mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun ga shaidu masu ban sha'awa daga wanda aka nada a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da wani mummunan abu da aka yi a shekarun 1980 da aka ce ya faru, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A lokaci guda, an ci gaba da gwagwarmayar siyasa da tashoshin da suka katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullum don ba da labari game da abin da ya faru a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya ƙulla, wanda ya ba FBI izinin gudanar da bincike na mako guda game da masu tuhuma.
Ford ta gaya wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata da cewa Kavanaugh ya yi fushi da ita a lokacin da take shan giya kuma ta yi ƙoƙari ta cire tufafinta don bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce a wata sanarwa mai cike da motsin rai cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Nielsen ya ce mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan taron a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya ba da rahoton yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samun damar samun lambobin kallo daga sauran tashoshin da ke nuna shi ba, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma yana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu kallon shirye-shirye a ofisoshinsa.
Don a sa shi a cikin hangen nesa, wannan adadi na kallo ne wanda ya yi daidai da wasan da aka buga a wasan NFL ko kuma bikin Oscar.
A cewar Nielsen, tashar Fox News, wadda masu sauraron ta yi farin ciki sosai da suka amince da za a naɗa Kavanaugh, ta yi fice a cikin dukan tashoshi da yawan masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron da ya ɗauki tsawon yini.
A lokacin da aka yi wannan taron, an yi amfani da 'yan jarida da yawa don yin magana da mutane game da wannan batun.
CBS na da miliyan 3.1 da NBC na da miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC na da miliyan 2.89 da CNN na da miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
Bayan sauraron wannan tambayar, mutane sun yi murna sosai.
Flake shi ne babban mutum a wasan kwaikwayon ranar Jumma'a.
Bayan da ofishin 'yan jam'iyyar Republican ta yi sanarwa cewa zai yi zabe ga Kavanaugh, an kama shi a gaban kyamarori na CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a, yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke ihu a kansa yayin da yake ƙoƙarin hawa lif don sauraron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya yi ta kallon ƙasa na tsawon minti da yawa yayin da ake yi masa ba'a, kuma CNN ta watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye.
Wata mace ta ce: "Ina tsaye a gabanka.
"Ka yi zaton zai gaya wa ƙasar gaskiya?"
Ya ce, "Kana da iko sosai, kuma mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya aika da wata sanarwa, kuma kafin a rufe ɗaki ya ce yana so ya faɗi ƙarin abubuwa a lokacin da ake sauraron kwamitin.
Bayan 'yan sa'o'i, duk gidajen talabijin sun yi taɗi a kai a kai, yayin da kwamitin shari'a ya shirya don yin zabe ko za a tura sunan Kavanaugh zuwa kuri'ar Majalisar Dattijai.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi zabe ne kawai a kan tabbacin cewa FBI za ta bincika zargin da aka yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat da ke da rinjaye a majalisar dattijai suka bukaci.
Flake ya yi imani da hakan ne daga tattaunawar da ya yi da abokinsa, Sanata Democrat Chris Coons.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci bayan haka, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Zaɓin Flake ya yi tasiri domin a bayyane yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su samu kuri'u ba don su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude binciken FBI game da zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
Firayim Ministan Burtaniya ya zargi masu sukarsa da "yin wasa da siyasa" da Brexit
Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirinta na barin EU da "yin wasa da siyasa" da makomar Birtaniya da kuma lalata bukatun kasa, a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
Firayim Ministan Birtaniya Theresa May za ta isa taron jam'iyyar Conservatives a Birmingham, Birtaniya a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
A wata hira da aka yi da Theresa May a shafin jaridar, tsohon ministan harkokin wajenta, Boris Johnson, ya nuna cewa ya yi hamayya da shirin da ta kira Chequers na Brexit, ya ce shawarar da Birtaniya da EU za su tara kudaden da juna za su biya "ainihin abin dariya ne".
Harin Wayde Sims: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson, wanda ake zargi da kashe dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani wanda ake zargi da harbi na Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekara 20.
An kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an tsare shi a kurkuku bisa zargin kisan kai da ba a kula da shi ba, in ji 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge.
Jami'ai sun saki bidiyon da ke nuna yadda Sims da Simpson suka yi faɗa, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin da ake gwagwarmaya.
'Yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin da aka yi wannan laifi kuma sun ce sun gano DNA na Simpson, kamar yadda kamfanin WAFB na CBS ya ruwaito.
Bayan an yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yi ikirarin kashe Wayde.
An ba da garantinsa a kan dala 350,000, in ji lauyan.
A ranar Juma'a, likitan kotun na East Baton Rouge Parish ya ba da rahoton cewa an kashe shi ne ta hanyar bindiga daga kai zuwa wuyansa.
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta ce wani jami'in 'yan sanda na jihar Louisiana, da kuma jami'ar 'yan sanda ta kudancin jihar, da kuma wasu 'yan'uwa a yankin sun taimaka wajen gudanar da binciken da ya kai ga kama shi.
Shugaban wasannin LSU, Joe Alleva, ya gode wa 'yan sanda na yankin don "kula da neman adalci".
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Wannan dan wasan mai tsayi na 6'8" ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya buga kwando a LSU.
Ya yi matsakaicin maki 5.6 da kuma sakewa 2.6 a wasan a kakar wasa ta karshe.
A safiyar Juma'a, kocin kwando na LSU, Will Wade, ya ce tawagar ta "ruɓe" kuma "ta yi mamaki" saboda mutuwar Wayde.
Wade ya ce: "Wannan shi ne abin da ake jin tsoro a kai a kai.
Tushen Volcano Yana Fitar da Ash a Birnin Mexico
Ash da aka yi daga dutsen mai suna Popocatepetl ya kai kudancin Mexico.
Cibiyar hana bala'i ta kasa ta yi gargadin jama'ar Mexico a ranar Asabar da ta gabata su guji zuwa wurin dutsen bayan da wani abu ya faru a cikin dutsen kuma an lura da fitar da iskar gas da toka 183 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Cibiyar ta lura da yanayin da kuma rawar jiki a cikin hanyoyi da yawa.
Hotunan da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna wasu ƙananan yadudduka na toka a kan katangar mota a unguwannin birnin Mexico kamar su Xochimilco.
Masu binciken ilimin geophysics sun lura da karuwar aikin da ake yi a cikin dutsen mai tsawo, wanda ke da nisan kilomita 72 kudu maso gabashin babban birnin kasar tun bayan girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.1 da ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumba na 2017.
Wannan dutsen mai suna "Don Goyo" ya fara aiki tun shekara ta 1994.
