Dole ne ƙungiyar Holt ta kasance a gaba a lokacin da suka zira kwallaye, kuma hanyar da suka yi wasa ta kai tsaye ta haifar da matsaloli masu yawa ga Rangers.
Scott Robinson ya yi tsalle, amma ya yi tsalle a gaban maƙasudin, bayan haka Alan Lithgow ya buga a waje da maƙasudin ba makawa bayan ya yi tsalle don ya buga Craig Halket's crossing header a gaban maƙasudin.
Ƙungiyar gida ta yi farin cikin barin Rangers su yi wasa a gabansu domin sun san za su iya ba da matsala ga waɗanda ba su yi ba a yanayin mutuwa.
