Yan wasan Rangers sun yi bugun jini, Livingston ya yi amfani da wani buɗewa, kuma Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun haɗa kai don su shirya shirin Menga, wanda ya yi taɓawa kuma ya ci daga tsakiyar filin.
