Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara taron zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan ne taron farko na Trump a cikin biyar da aka shirya a makon gobe, ciki har da taron a wurare masu son Trump kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da alkalin kotun da aka nada Trump don kujerar da ta rage a kotun koli, Trump na kokarin samar da goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar watan Nuwamba saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar hadarin rasa iko da majalisa lokacin da aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron zaben Trump a West Virginia a yau, kuma yaya kake ganin hakan a kan layi?
Za a gudanar da taron zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a tsakar dare (lokacin Danish) tsakanin Asabar, 29 ga Nuwamba, da Lahadi, 30 ga Nuwamba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana a kan sauraron da ake yi a wannan makon game da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli. Taron ya kasance mai rikitarwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, kuma an dakatar da zaɓe na Majalisar Dattijai na tabbatarwa na mako guda yayin da FBI ke binciken masu zargin.
Amma babban burin wannan taro na zaben na samar da karfin gwiwa ga 'yan jam'iyyar Republican da ke fuskantar babban zaben watan Nuwamba.
Wasu daga cikin masu fafatawa a yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce za a gudanar da taron biyar na mako mai zuwa don "haɓaka ƙarfin masu sa kai da kuma goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma faɗaɗa rinjayen da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa yana da muhimmanci sosai ga tsarinsa, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda ya yiwu yanzu da muke shiga cikin wannan lokacin da ake neman zabe", wani mai magana da yawun yakin Trump, wanda ba a ambaci sunansa ba, ya gaya wa Reuters.
Ana sa ran taron da za a yi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling zai jawo hankalin magoya bayan Trump daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a yi ta yin ta da kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe sama da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba shi ƙarin ƙarfi a cikin kuri'un", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin ilimin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
