Ƙungiyar daga Ibrox ta kasance bayan nasarar da ta fara a kan harsashin bayan 4-1 a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma ƙungiyar Gary Holt ta ba Gerrard na biyu kawai a cikin wasanni 18 a matsayin mai horar da shi.
Menga ya kai ga minti bakwai kafin hutu, wanda wani rukunin 'yan sanda ba su iya amsawa ba.
Yan wasan Rangers sun koma matsayi na shida, yayin da Livingston ya hau matsayi na uku bayan Hibernian, inda kawai ya ci nasara.
Kuma akwai wasu labarai masu ban tsoro da za su zo Rangers, da cewa alkalin layi Calum Spence ya bukaci a yi masa magani bayan da wani abu da aka jefa a kansa ya yi masa rauni, wanda ya fito daga sashen raƙuman wuta.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin saitin da ya kai wasan karshe na Betfed Cup ta hanyar wuce Ayr.
