'Yan wasan Rangers ne suka fi samun ƙwallon ƙafa, amma Livingston ya fi yin nasara.
Ya kamata su ci minti biyu a wasan lokacin da Menga ta fara wasan da Scott Pittman ya ci Allan McGregor, amma ƙoƙarin dan wasan tsakiya ya wuce.
Wani bugun jini daga Keaghan Jacobs ya kai ga Captain Craig Halkett, amma mai tsaron gidansa Alan Lithgow ya wuce ta baya.
Duk da haka, 'yan wasan Rangers sun ci gaba da yin nasara, amma sun yi amfani da bege fiye da iyawa a wasan kai hari.
Aƙalla Alfredo Morales bai yi farin ciki ba sa'ad da Alkalin Kotun Steven Thomson ya ƙi amincewa da bukatar da ɗan ƙasar Colombia ya yi na neman fansa a lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka haɗu bayan wasan da ya yi na kwata-kwata.
Rangers sun yi nasarar harbi biyu kawai a raga a farkon rabin rabin, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Rangers Liam Kelly bai da matsala tare da bugun kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma bugun baya na Ovie Ejarias.
Ko da yake buɗewar Livy a minti na 34 ba zato ba tsammani ba ne, dole ne a ce an yi ta ne don ƙoƙarin da suka yi.
Har yanzu, 'yan tsaron sun kasa magance yanayin kisa a cikin zurfin Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya tura kwallon ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya dauki lokaci don neman Menga wanda zai iya jefa shi cikin sauƙi a raga.
A lokacin hutu, Gerrard Coulibaly ya maye gurbin Ryan Kent, wanda kusan nan take ya ba da gudummawa lokacin da mai kunnawa ya tura kwallon zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai kyau ya gudu daga matsayinsa don toshewa.
Amma, rashin nasarar da Livingston ya samu ya sa ya yi wasa a kan takardunsu da kuma manyan kwallaye da yawa a filin daga Lithgow da Halkett.
Ma'aikatan Holt na iya faɗaɗa jagorar a ƙarshen wasan, amma McGregor ya ƙi Jacobs da tabbaci kafin Lithgow ya ci gaba da gaba da gaba.
Glenn Middleton, wanda ya maye gurbin Rangers, ya sake neman a yi masa hukunci a kan hukuncin da ya yi a baya bayan ya yi wa Jacobs horo, amma Alkalin Shari'a Thomson ya yi watsi da wannan.
Littafin Shekara: Wanda Ya kirkiro Geiger Count
Yanzu ga wani shafi daga littafin tarihi "Sunday Morning": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka gabata a yau idan muka ƙidaya... ranar da aka haifi mai suna Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiri wata hanyar ganowa da kuma auna radiation, wani abu da zai kai ga yin amfani da na'urar da ake kira geiger counting.
Mai ƙididdigar geiger ya zama wani ɓangare na kimiyya da al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka gani a fim din "Bells of Coronado" na 1950, inda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka taka rawar gani a matsayin masana kimiyya na manoma:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar ƙidaya ne da ake amfani da ita don gano abubuwa masu yaduwa kamar su uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da kwayoyin suke yi a cikin ma'adinai".
Evans: "Ka daina, yanzu ne ya soma!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, kwanaki biyu kafin ya cika shekara 63.
