Lt. Col. da kuma firist Bernard Wann sun lashe wannan tsari a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da aka kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani mai harbi ya kashe shi kuma ba a san cewa ya lashe lambar yabo mafi girma a cikin sojojin Ingila ba.
A ranar Asabar, akalla 'ya'yansa biyu ne suka fallasa wani a wani biki a Rushden, Northhamptonshire.
