A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa a kan Canal de Saint-Quentin "cikin hazo mai zurfi da kuma bindigogi da kuma bindigogi masu ƙarfi", in ji The London Gazette.
Daga baya, ya gudu zuwa gaba, ya ja-goranci mutanensa da "babban ƙarfin hali" kafin ya kai wa wani rukunin bindiga hari shi kaɗai kuma ya hana wasu guns uku.
